7
00:01:00,193 --> 00:01:02,286
<i>I don't give a goddamn
what the story is.</i>

8
00:01:02,362 --> 00:01:03,920
<i>He went on television.</i>

9
00:01:05,965 --> 00:01:07,728
<i>I have not. I've
already ordered Connally,</i>

